name: Routine for registering new customers on the picpay ecommerce platform.
description:
Being a customer interested in selling my products on the PicPay platform
    I must be able to make a new registration or access, if you already have access

elements.name: Create a complete pf or pj register

steps.name: I am on the home page (Background)
I fill in the your access data
select the 'Pessoa física' of your account
after you fill in the data about you
select the '14 dias' and fill in company infos and your 'Arte e Antiguidades'
you must confirm the data and complete the registration
